snippet.title: Doom Fighters Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the new gameplay never seen in the classic Doom. A beat em up with 3D player model with cool animations to beat the monsters in many ways, adding an exclusive experience for doom players that will taste the best of the gameplays in the doom modding community.

Download Mod:
https://www.moddb.com/mods/doom-fighters/downloads/doom-fighters

Follow me at:
https://web.facebook.com/edy.pagaza.gaming

Music from:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YiyEKq63Y0Q
